description: The run-off election is seen as a fierce liberal-conservative battle for the country's future.
title: Poland election: Clash of ideals as voters choose head of state
title_page: Poland election: Clash of ideals as voters choose head of state - BBC News
maintext: "Everything is in your hands," he said on Friday. "This [electoral victory] is really at your fingertips. I want to tell you 'now or never' because this Law and Justice road roller will try to run over everything and the next election could be very difficult."
